Welcome to the documentation of CEINMS

Welcome to CEINMS. The software for neuromusculoskeletal modeling. CEINMS has moved to opensource development so that the community can grow and improve. In this documentation we will guide you through the installation process, debugging of your installation, tutorials and available plugins.

Note

This project is under active development.
